caption.text:
Okay so I've been tagged by @gentamaulanaman to do #10bucketlist at 2015 since a loong time ago. Sorry dude, I just get my mood now haha.

1. Get a good score and if I could, get 4.0 as my GPA. Okay so I got distracted at the 1st semester because of those "maba-mabaan" stuff. Therefore, I couldn't really focus and enjoy my lectures. So my goal for the 2nd semester is to study as much as I can. Not just to get good grades but also to ged lots of knowledges. Somehow, study could be fun!

2. Do a historical trip to museums all over Jakarta.

3. Read as many books as I can!

4. Join many organization that fit my talents and my hobbies. Oh and also volunteering in places.

5. Learn many foreign languages, such as French, Arabian, and Korean. At least by the end of the year, I could speak fluently.

6. Get closer to all people at HI UI and friends from another major.

7. Become a better person.

8. Get a half-time job that enable me to get my own income. So then, I could spend them to "hedon dan berfoya-foya" wkwkwk. Oh and some scholarships would be nice.

9. Go abroad, at least once! And for free!

10. Ehe he. I am open for any wish (?)
This is us, from beginning till the end. Sadly, something's missing there. #superlatepost #endofmabalife #bukanmabalagi #ospekselesaai

1. Fullname: Juni Arina Khairiyati. Sometimes I said to people that although my name is Juni, I was born in August. And lots of people believe it.
2 is my lucky number perhaps?
3. Love turquoise, orange, and light brown.
4. I really like orange, mint, coffe, bubble gum, and cotton candy flavour.
5. I have a dream to become a movie director one day and make my own TV channel.
6. Huge fan of Sherlock, Harry Potter, and Avatar Aang + Korra
7.  Love sweet food (CAKES) and hate super spicy food.
8. Easy to be tricked. People gonna tell a lie or a joke, and usually I believe it...
9. LOVE LOVE LOVE reading! But now, due to a busy time of college student, I rarely read a book anymore..
10. I really wanna go to England someday!
11. I love coffe and milk tea
12. I want to design my own room and house later
13. I like art and design!
14. I hate people that spit in public
15. I HATE snake.
16. I had a dream to become an astronaut, I even kept NASA phone number on my cellphone
17. I always want to learn sign language, violin, dance, and drum.
18. I want to open my own ice cream and chocolate shop, so I could eat then as much as I want
19. Sometimes I have this crazy idea to dye my hair blue.
20. I always like to see a guy that wear black shirt with folded arm, or turtleneck, or a guy that wear a headset or earphone for works. 
That's it! :))
